WEBVTT

00:00.500 --> 00:02.960
Katie, I just heard the news.

00:03.195 --> 00:05.462
I sold my book proposal!

00:05.491 --> 00:06.456
They're going to pay me
to write my book!

00:06.542 --> 00:07.925
Congratulations!

00:07.977 --> 00:09.610
And the publishers are sending
a cash advance and everything!

00:09.695 --> 00:10.861
Amazing!

00:10.913 --> 00:12.262
And I thought of a title...
"John Stuart Mill

00:12.298 --> 00:13.513
and the Consequences of a Thoroughgoing

00:13.599 --> 00:15.148
Empiricist Outlook!"

00:15.234 --> 00:16.917
Help me out here. I'm losing steam.

00:17.002 --> 00:17.834
I sold my book!

00:17.920 --> 00:20.103
Yay!

00:20.189 --> 00:21.071
Let's have a special dinner tonight.

00:21.156 --> 00:22.239
It'll just be us.

00:22.291 --> 00:23.590
And Anna-Kat.

00:23.676 --> 00:24.808
And the other two.

00:24.860 --> 00:25.892
It'll be a regular dinner.

00:25.978 --> 00:27.160
Yay!

00:27.246 --> 00:28.495
That sounds great.
I'll... I'll see you back here

00:28.564 --> 00:29.463
- in a couple of hours.
- Oh.

00:29.548 --> 00:30.380
But you just got home.

00:30.466 --> 00:31.548
Where are you going?

00:31.617 --> 00:33.617
Yeah, I-I want to get a jump on my book.

00:33.702 --> 00:35.686
You can't do that from the study?

00:35.721 --> 00:38.622
It's, uh, just... I have to go, uh...

00:38.674 --> 00:42.359
There's so much noise here.

00:47.316 --> 00:48.398
Potential noise.

00:48.484 --> 00:49.866
I'll be back for dinner.

00:53.732 --> 00:55.787
Katie: <i>Greg has been acting
odd lately...</i>

00:55.881 --> 00:57.564
<i>uncomfortable and avoiding eye contact,</i>

00:57.650 --> 00:59.666
<i>like when he has those dreams
where me and his mom</i>

00:59.752 --> 01:00.867
<i>are the same person.</i>

01:00.953 --> 01:02.419
<i>What is going on with him?</i>

01:03.555 --> 01:05.052
Hey.

01:05.608 --> 01:06.773
I don't have much time.

01:06.859 --> 01:08.185
I told my wife I'd be home for dinner.

01:08.327 --> 01:10.460
Oh, okay. Want a drink?

01:10.546 --> 01:11.805
Yeah.

