05:23.098 --> 05:25.732
Why are we still in our clothes?

05:25.784 --> 05:29.336
What happened to us last night?

05:29.371 --> 05:33.373
I don't remember anything after
those Blazeball shots you ordered.

05:33.459 --> 05:34.541
Why?

05:34.593 --> 05:38.345
I was feeling nervous about Celeste
and I was trying to break the tension.

05:39.715 --> 05:42.766
I got a pedicure?

05:42.851 --> 05:45.519
Oh, honey, that's not all you got.

05:50.059 --> 05:53.143
I haven't given a hickey
since high school.

05:53.228 --> 05:55.779
Well, you made up for lost time.

05:55.864 --> 05:57.447
I can't be seen like this.

05:57.533 --> 05:58.532
Wow.

05:58.567 --> 06:01.034
