06:48.713 --> 06:49.745
Oh.

06:51.783 --> 06:54.033
Flashes of the night are going
to begin to come back to you.

06:54.118 --> 06:58.571
Usually it's the stuff
that makes you go, "Why?!"

07:00.508 --> 07:03.092
Oh, move. It's my turn.

07:03.177 --> 07:04.093
[Gasps]

07:07.966 --> 07:11.183
Oh, no.

07:11.269 --> 07:13.085
My jacket's ruined.

07:13.171 --> 07:14.940
Wait a minute.
I'm remembering something.

07:14.965 --> 07:16.239
What?

07:16.274 --> 07:18.875
Last night I came up with
the perfect opening line

07:18.927 --> 07:21.727
for my book. I wrote it on a napkin.

07:21.813 --> 07:23.112
It's not here.

07:23.147 --> 07:24.497
I got to find that napkin.

07:24.582 --> 07:27.383
Without the perfect opening,
I have no book!

07:27.468 --> 07:29.869
Oh, this feels so good.

07:29.954 --> 07:30.870
I'm going to go call Celeste.

07:30.955 --> 07:31.921
Maybe she'll remember something.

07:33.808 --> 07:36.208
Taylor: Hey, Katie.

07:36.277 --> 07:37.793
What did you just call me?

07:37.879 --> 07:39.095
Katie.

07:39.147 --> 07:40.446
After last night,
you told me to call you that.

07:40.531 --> 07:41.447
Remember?

07:44.736 --> 07:47.737
Taylor?

07:47.789 --> 07:52.224
Are you awake?

07:52.293 --> 07:53.242
Mom?

07:55.263 --> 07:58.314
You're so pretty.

08:01.302 --> 08:04.070
