08:11.713 --> 08:16.082
I want us to be best friends.

08:16.167 --> 08:19.652
Call me Katie from now on, okay?

08:19.737 --> 08:23.539
I remember that.

08:23.591 --> 08:25.107
Totally.

08:25.143 --> 08:26.225
Mm-hmm.

08:29.213 --> 08:31.063
You used to be such a good liar.

08:31.149 --> 08:32.698
It's sad.

08:35.669 --> 08:38.220
♪

08:38.272 --> 08:40.239
All right, Anna-Kat and I
have been talking.

08:40.308 --> 08:42.207
She's gotten past the puppy,
and we figured out a gift

08:42.293 --> 08:43.893
