08:43.945 --> 08:45.661
a trampoline. You in?

08:45.697 --> 08:46.746
Absolutely.

08:46.831 --> 08:47.713
You know what's cute?

08:47.799 --> 08:49.598
A puppy on a trampoline.

08:49.634 --> 08:50.783
You know what's a drain

08:50.852 --> 08:52.918
