already limited resources?

08:53.004 --> 08:55.638
A puppy.

08:55.723 --> 08:56.939
Fine.

08:57.025 --> 08:59.125
Well, we should've asked for
the trampoline last night.

08:59.210 --> 09:02.862
Mom got super drunk and would've
given us whatever we wanted.

09:02.947 --> 09:06.465
But this morning she doesn't
remember a thing, so...

09:06.534 --> 09:09.452
Maybe we did ask Mom
for something last night,

09:09.487 --> 09:12.288
and she just
doesn't remember saying yes.

09:12.373 --> 09:13.589
Wait, when did we do that?

09:13.641 --> 09:17.159
We didn't, but we're going
to say we did.

09:20.014 --> 09:22.652
Ohhh. [Laughs weakly]

09:24.452 --> 09:26.035
