09:26.087 --> 09:29.438
[Sighs] Come on,
I'll explain as we walk.

09:32.043 --> 09:35.511
Mom, we need to talk to you
about something.

09:35.563 --> 09:36.946
[Sighs]

09:36.981 --> 09:38.914
Remember last night when you
came home from celebrating

09:38.966 --> 09:40.416
with Dad and you promised us a present

09:40.501 --> 09:42.651
because he sold his book?

09:42.687 --> 09:43.953
Totally.

09:43.988 --> 09:45.538
So, when do we pick out our...

09:45.623 --> 09:47.890
Puppy!

09:47.942 --> 09:49.158
Puppy, huh?

09:49.193 --> 09:51.794
Mm-hmm. That's what
you said we could have.

09:51.829 --> 09:54.180
Okay, no matter what state I was in,

09:54.265 --> 09:55.481
I would never agree to a puppy.

09:55.566 --> 09:56.816
Maybe a 15-year-old rescue dog

09:56.884 --> 09:59.952
who's got a few months left
in it, but never a puppy.

10:00.038 --> 10:02.138
Wait! No, no. She meant trampoline!

10:02.223 --> 10:06.592
