she's a weird kid!

10:06.677 --> 10:08.994
- [Door closes]
- Well, we tried.

10:09.080 --> 10:10.279
Right, guys?

10:13.084 --> 10:14.450
- [Sighs]
- Yeah.

10:14.519 --> 10:16.619
I looked for that
stupid napkin everywhere.

10:16.654 --> 10:17.987
I'm so itchy.

10:18.072 --> 10:20.506
It's probably your turtleneck
rubbing against your hickeys.

10:20.591 --> 10:22.942
- You know about those?
- I watched it go down.

10:23.027 --> 10:25.661
They left more of a mark on me
than they did on you.

10:25.713 --> 10:27.630
[Lady Gaga's "Poker Face" plays]

10:27.665 --> 10:30.099
How many hickeys is she up to?

10:30.184 --> 10:36.722
Oh, well, one for every "hand-jive"
Greg does, so, uh, six.

10:36.808 --> 10:41.210
Keep it going, girl!
Mama needs a few nights off!

10:41.295 --> 10:42.528
You remember all that,

10:42.597 --> 10:43.946
but you don't remember
the opening line of my book?

10:43.981 --> 10:46.365
You scribbled something down on
a napkin and you yelled,

10:46.451 --> 10:48.584
"I'm a literary God!"

10:48.669 --> 10:51.103
And then you heard Lady Gaga and
you ran back to the dance floor

10:51.189 --> 10:53.522
