11:16.414 --> 11:18.681
So, you two just decided to go out big?

11:18.733 --> 11:20.983
Yep. Just the two of us.

11:21.018 --> 11:22.701
Just me and Greg. All night.

11:22.770 --> 11:24.253
Me and him.

11:24.305 --> 11:26.155
Me and my man. [Snickering]

11:26.190 --> 11:28.491
No one else?

11:28.576 --> 11:30.376
Not that I remember.

11:30.461 --> 11:34.063
Well, let me see if I can help
you fill in the missing details.

11:34.115 --> 11:35.247
Does this ring any bells?

11:37.435 --> 11:38.884
Where did you get that?

11:38.970 --> 11:40.736
Celeste's Instagram.

11:40.771 --> 11:42.738
