but it was only for a minute,

11:49.981 --> 11:51.931
and I gave her the cold shoulder
and I moved on.

11:52.016 --> 11:53.933
Oh. Which shoulder? This shoulder?

11:54.018 --> 11:56.068
The one she has her head on?

11:56.154 --> 11:58.120
So busted.

11:58.206 --> 11:59.588
Can I take a look at that?

11:59.624 --> 12:01.357
Last night is a little blurry.

12:01.392 --> 12:03.526
I just need to see exactly
what I'm guilty of.

12:03.578 --> 12:07.179
Here, here, and here,

12:07.248 --> 12:08.380
you're guilty of being a bad friend.

12:08.466 --> 12:09.431
Does that help you?

12:09.467 --> 12:11.817
Okay, obviously I saw Celeste.

12:11.903 --> 12:12.785
But I didn't want to.

12:12.870 --> 12:14.203
It's all Greg's fault.

12:14.238 --> 12:15.788
He kept in touch with her.

12:15.873 --> 12:18.340
You drank a shot off her belly.

12:18.426 --> 12:20.809
It was understood that
you weren't gonna see her.

12:20.895 --> 12:22.444
There was a ban on Celeste.

12:22.480 --> 12:24.713
Just like there's a ban on us
going to Murray's Frozen Yogurt

12:24.749 --> 12:26.882
because you had into a
disagreement over the definition

12:26.968 --> 12:28.300
of "unlimited toppings."

12:28.369 --> 12:30.569
I was one punch away from a free yogurt.

12:30.655 --> 12:32.588
But we don't go there
out of respect for you.

12:32.623 --> 12:34.006
But it looks like you have
no respect for me.

12:34.091 --> 12:35.424
Don't be like that.

12:35.476 --> 12:37.743
In my defense, you weren't
even supposed to find out.

12:37.828 --> 12:39.161
Typical Katie Otto.

12:39.213 --> 12:40.379
Excuse me?

12:40.464 --> 12:41.680
You know, when I was
just getting to know you,

12:41.766 --> 12:43.465
I thought your whole
"me first" thing was charming.

12:43.517 --> 12:45.434
But it's not. You tune out anything

12:45.486 --> 12:46.518
that doesn't have to do with you.

12:46.587 --> 12:47.786
You're so selfish.

12:47.872 --> 12:49.338
You do what you want, when you want,

12:49.423 --> 12:51.473
without giving a damn
about anybody else.

12:51.559 --> 12:53.075
- Whoa.
- You want to talk selfish?

12:53.110 --> 12:54.190
Please!

12:54.215 --> 12:55.294
You're the one who made
your friends choose sides

12:55.379 --> 12:56.679
when your marriage fell apart

12:56.714 --> 12:58.130
because you couldn't keep it
in your skinny jeans!

12:58.216 --> 12:59.348
Right, Doris?

12:59.400 --> 13:01.700
This iced tea is good.

13:01.786 --> 13:03.836
- That's how you feel?
- Mm-hmm.

13:03.921 --> 13:05.254
Fine.

13:05.306 --> 13:06.805
You know what? Be friends with Celeste,

13:06.891 --> 13:08.307
because you're not friends with me.

13:08.392 --> 13:09.692
I'm done with you.

13:09.777 --> 13:10.993
Ditto!

13:14.515 --> 13:16.015
"Ditto"?

13:16.100 --> 13:17.983
Not a strong ender.

13:18.069 --> 13:19.368
♪

13:22.873 --> 13:24.206
What are you doing?

13:24.292 --> 13:26.475
Maybe I threw the napkin
in here when I was drunk.

13:26.527 --> 13:28.143
Mm. That's a stretch.

13:28.195 --> 13:29.478
Hey, we found your bra in the fridge.

13:29.530 --> 13:30.663
Anything is possible.

13:30.748 --> 13:33.198
Last night created such a mess.

13:33.284 --> 13:34.800
I just got in a huge fight with Angela.

13:34.885 --> 13:36.635
She called me selfish.

13:36.721 --> 13:37.753
This is all your fault.

13:37.838 --> 13:39.338
- My fault?
- Yep.

13:39.423 --> 13:41.590
You just had to be friends with Celeste.

13:41.676 --> 13:43.142
And you just had to have me
hang out with her.

13:43.227 --> 13:45.227
You're right. I did have
to be friends with Celeste,

13:45.263 --> 13:47.646
because I needed
a sounding board for my book

13:47.732 --> 13:50.566
and every time I asked you to be
that for me, you wouldn't.

13:50.601 --> 13:52.768
That is not selfish.

13:52.853 --> 13:55.571
That is just... self-preservation.

13:55.606 --> 13:59.108
Katie, I know it's unpleasant
to hear, but Angela's not wrong.

13:59.193 --> 14:01.360
Sometimes, you can be selfish.

14:04.282 --> 14:06.168
I am not selfish!

14:06.193 --> 14:07.303
[Retches]

14:07.328 --> 14:09.084
<i>Is that the sound of
my hungover husband throwing up</i>

14:09.109 --> 14:11.137
<i>in the bathroom? I should help him.</i>

14:11.162 --> 14:12.338
[Retches]

14:12.423 --> 14:14.303
<i>I'm sure he wants his privacy.</i>

14:18.008 --> 14:20.359
Look at me, making you a snack.

14:20.421 --> 14:23.461
Not just any snack...
apples with peanut butter.

14:23.546 --> 14:25.323
And I cut them into little boats.

14:25.464 --> 14:27.698
- Would a selfish person do that?
- No, Mama.

14:27.762 --> 14:28.831
Of course not.

14:28.901 --> 14:32.112
Then again, I'm your kid
and if you don't feed me, I die.

14:32.456 --> 14:35.246
Eat this and go play
with your brother and sister.

14:35.331 --> 14:37.214
I can't. They're not talking to me.

14:37.266 --> 14:38.649
What's going on?

14:38.684 --> 14:40.317
They're mad because
I asked you for what I wanted

14:40.386 --> 14:42.753
instead of asking you
for what we all wanted.

14:42.805 --> 14:45.990
Mm. Puppy instead of a trampoline?

14:46.058 --> 14:49.260
Well, you can see why they
might be a little mad, right?

14:49.328 --> 14:51.295
But I just did what you always do...

14:51.364 --> 14:52.880
get what you want and then tell
the other people

14:52.949 --> 14:54.698
to go fudge themselves.

14:54.767 --> 14:55.883
Yes.

14:55.968 --> 14:57.536
That's what Mommy says.

15:02.242 --> 15:03.825
- Greg!
- [Gasps]

15:03.893 --> 15:05.276
- What?
- [Sighs]

15:05.361 --> 15:06.460
You weren't moving.

15:06.545 --> 15:07.928
I thought you were dead.

15:08.014 --> 15:10.564
[Sighs] I'm trying to
re-create my lost opening line.

15:10.650 --> 15:11.999
You want me to help you?

15:12.084 --> 15:13.050
You don't want to.

15:13.085 --> 15:14.335
I know.

15:14.403 --> 15:16.804
But the difference is now,
I want to want to.

15:16.889 --> 15:18.372
I'm sorry that I didn't take an interest

15:18.457 --> 15:19.873
in what you were working on.

15:19.959 --> 15:21.425
Thank you. That means a lot.

15:21.510 --> 15:23.227
I'm not even going to mention
what's going on with me,

15:23.262 --> 15:24.862
because that would be selfish.

15:24.947 --> 15:27.514
And this moment is about you.

15:27.600 --> 15:28.799
I appreciate that.

15:28.851 --> 15:30.851
Maybe if I close my eyes
and clear my mind,

15:30.937 --> 15:32.236
the line will come back to me.

15:34.674 --> 15:37.608
[As Greg] Gee, Katie,
you seem kind of blue.

15:37.677 --> 15:39.343
What's going on with you?

15:42.098 --> 15:44.815
[Normal voice] Maybe talking about me
will jog your memory.

15:44.900 --> 15:46.533
I'm sorry.

15:46.619 --> 15:48.636
I usually go to Angela
with this sort of thing.

15:48.721 --> 15:50.371
I need to get Angela back
so she can tell me

15:50.456 --> 15:51.605
how to get Angela back.

15:51.691 --> 15:53.324
- Just call her.
- I tried to.

15:53.376 --> 15:55.009
She's not picking up the phone.
She's avoiding me.

15:55.094 --> 15:56.977
Then go find her at the retreat.

15:57.063 --> 15:59.146
Oh, my God, the retreat.

15:59.231 --> 16:00.531
How do you know about that?

16:00.583 --> 16:01.932
Celeste told me because
she has the kids all week.

16:01.968 --> 16:04.785
Oh, if only I'd listened better,
I would know that.

16:04.870 --> 16:07.204
[Tranquil music plays]

16:12.161 --> 16:14.044
Hey.

16:14.096 --> 16:18.666
I came to apologize.

16:18.751 --> 16:19.967
No, I can't apologize?

16:20.052 --> 16:21.518
Shhhhh!

16:21.554 --> 16:25.155
- Don't shush me!
- We're in a silent retreat!

16:25.241 --> 16:28.542
- Silent like no talking?
- Shhh!

16:28.627 --> 16:30.194
Do that one more time
and see what happens.

16:30.229 --> 16:32.696
[Whispering] Again, you are
totally self-focused.

16:32.732 --> 16:34.715
You have no awareness
of what's going on around you.

16:34.800 --> 16:37.134
I am trying to apologize.

16:37.186 --> 16:38.819
Well, you're doing a bad job.

16:38.904 --> 16:41.705
Just leave before you get me kicked out.

16:54.994 --> 16:57.455
[Exhales]

17:18.517 --> 17:20.579
__

17:24.661 --> 17:26.833
__

17:33.614 --> 17:36.617
__

17:42.604 --> 17:45.086
__

18:14.667 --> 18:16.133
I'm sorry, too.

18:16.218 --> 18:17.101
You forgive me?

18:17.870 --> 18:19.953
♪

18:25.811 --> 18:28.112
You want to join me?

18:28.197 --> 18:30.164
I'm not suddenly someone else.

18:30.249 --> 18:32.082
[Chuckles] Right.

18:40.292 --> 18:43.360
So, Angela's good as long as
I don't see Celeste

18:43.395 --> 18:45.445
and you two sneak around
behind my back again.

18:45.531 --> 18:46.530
I'm fine with that.

18:46.582 --> 18:47.865
I was gonna miss sneaking around.

18:47.917 --> 18:50.767
It makes me feel dangerous,
like when I swallow my gum.

18:50.853 --> 18:53.570
Did you ever remember the
opening line to your book?

18:53.622 --> 18:54.571
Gone forever.

18:54.623 --> 18:55.956
Those words of genius

18:56.041 --> 18:59.560
and why my toenails are painted
remain a mystery.

18:59.645 --> 19:01.662
Oh, wait a second. I know that color.

19:01.747 --> 19:04.097
That is Princess Pop Pink.

19:04.183 --> 19:06.099
It's from Anna-Kat's Make-Up Molly Kit.

19:14.593 --> 19:16.827
Shhh!

19:18.697 --> 19:20.697
Shhh!

19:22.501 --> 19:24.518
Shhh!

19:24.603 --> 19:25.903
Daddy?

19:25.938 --> 19:28.105
What are you doing awake?

19:28.157 --> 19:30.073
Go back to sleep.

19:30.109 --> 19:33.994
Well, now that you're here,
let's do spa day!

19:34.079 --> 19:36.430
I've never wanted to do anything more!

19:40.386 --> 19:43.437
I need some tissue
to separate your toes.

19:47.026 --> 19:48.091
Will this do?

19:48.160 --> 19:49.326
Perfect.

19:53.883 --> 19:55.966
Anna-Kat, do you have that napkin

19:56.001 --> 19:57.668
from my spa day last night?

19:57.753 --> 20:01.088
If I find it for you,
can I have a trampoline?

20:01.173 --> 20:02.089
Anything.

20:06.228 --> 20:07.978
Guys, you can't be mad at me anymore!

20:08.013 --> 20:10.062
I got us a trampoline!

20:10.960 --> 20:12.015
Eh.

20:18.481 --> 20:20.564
Oh, God, I remember everything.

20:20.650 --> 20:24.869
♪ I wanna feel the heat with somebody ♪

20:24.904 --> 20:29.457
♪ Yeah, I wanna dance with somebody ♪

20:29.542 --> 20:32.827
♪ With somebody who loves me ♪

20:32.912 --> 20:35.713
♪ Oh, oh ♪

20:35.748 --> 20:36.747
♪ Dance ♪

20:36.833 --> 20:37.998
♪ Come on, baby ♪

20:38.084 --> 20:39.834
[Laughs]

20:39.919 --> 20:42.303
- ♪ Dance ♪
- ♪ Ooh! ♪

20:42.388 --> 20:43.587
♪ Yeah ♪

